snippet.title: FIFA 19 | The Journey: Champions | Official Story Trailer ft. Hunter, Neymar, de Bruyne, Dybala
snippet.description:
Alex Hunter is back for The Journey: Champions in FIFA 19, and he's joined by playable characters Danny Williams and Kim Hunter. Chase UEFA Champions League and FIFA Women's World Cup France 2019(TM) glory as you experience three distinct stories in the finale of The Journey. Learn more: http://x.ea.com/49170

Pre-order FIFA 19 now: http://x.ea.com/49171

Subscribe to see more official FIFA 19 trailers: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.
